As one of Acuity Brands’ leading products in lighting solutions, Peerless offers the latest technologies providing the latest in quality illumination for its clients and their surroundings. Peerless’ lighting solutions offers products designed for office areas, schools, transportation stations, and other public settings. These same products feature stylishness, visual comfort, and sophisticated elements of design incorporated in their architecture. Peerless lighting solutions present the client with practicality, low initial investments, quick shipping, ease of installation, and cross-product integration, all of which are included in Peerless’ Quickship program.

 Peerless focuses on product research principally to further design and develop the most superior lighting solutions of the industry for its clients. Peerless capitalizes on information regarding the client’s physical and mental benefits derived from proper lighting. This same information is also used to design precise and accurate instruments which gauge lighting levels so as to aid lighting solution experts in predicting the probable effects of product design.

 Each and every one of Peerless’ products is designed with only the strictest standards in mind; all product aspects are meticulously scrutinized, from visual aesthetics, efficiency of performance, ease of installation and maintenance, and general costs of long-term upkeep. This approach of Peerless in maintaining its ideals has led to Peerless in leading the industry in sustainable lighting solutions.

 Peerless is also known to maintain close relationships with its clients by being open, considerate, and proactive in helping clients in issues regarding lighting solutions and by providing regular seminars which focus on sharing knowledge regarding lighting solutions to the general public.
